OL,3,CSouthend's Grade II-listed Kursaal
OL,4,Cadded to 'endangered' building list
OL,6,FThe Kursaal in Southend-on-Sea in
OL,7,FEssex has been ranked among the most
OL,8,F"endangered" Victorian buildings by a
OL,9,Fcharity dedicated to their
OL,10,Fpreservation.
OL,12,FThe venue which is located close to
OL,13,Fseafront is believed to be the world's
OL,14,Ffirst purpose-built amusement park
OL,15,Fwith a disused circus, ballroom,
OL,16,Farcade, dining hall, billiard room,
OL,17,Fzoo and ice rink.
