OL,3,CSouthend's Grade II-listed Kursaal
OL,4,Cadded to 'endangered' building list
OL,6,FRhys Jones said the list was "a
OL,7,Ftestament to the excitement, variety
OL,8,Fand invention of the Victorian Age".
OL,9,F"How terrifying to see buildings I
OL,10,Fhave known, loved or used all my life
OL,11,Fin Southend and Cardiff in need of
OL,12,Frescue," he added.J"But come on. Look
OL,13,Fat the character on display here. They
OL,14,Fall add colour and story to any urban
OL,15,Flandscape.J"Their restoration and
OL,16,Freuse make huge commercial sense. They
OL,17,Fare attractions in themselves. They
OL,18,Fare already destinations. They should
OL,19,Fbe part of local pride.J"What do we
OL,20,Fwant? A parking lot? A faceless block
OL,21,Fin their place? A slew of new carbon
OL,22,Fpollution? When they have so much
OL,23,Fcolour, continuity and history on
OL,24,Ftheir side already?"
